title: Spookles, for an "Unofficial Doodrivative' Badge
body:
Doodle ID for unusually bias kudos: #474
Doodle ID for usually bia kudos: #1920

Discourse: https://forum.doodles.app/t/spookle-unofficial-doodrivative-proposal/672/

Rationale: 
We were inspired by Doodles to create our own quirky and spooky take on the Doodleverse. The Halloween project sparked a passion in us to create more and also give back to the Doodle community which has inspired and encouraged us. Spookles is our genesis collection of 300 1:1s and we hope to receive the 'Unofficial Doodrivative' badge. In return, we will share 3% royalties to Doodlebank and provide 30 free mints to Doodlers!

Benefits to doods:
1. 240 WL reserved for Doodles owners.
2. 30 free mints raffle for the 240 doodles White-listers.
3. If demand is high, we might have a public raffle for doodler slots.
4. Doodlers will also get WL access to future non-doodles, derivative projects our team works on.

Timeline: If we meet the minimum quorum and receive majority vote, we will be waiting for the founders' feedback. 

At the moment we have:
The art 85% ready
The website + the minting system 90%
The community wallet 100% ready

Information: 300, 1 of 1 Spookles NFTs
240 WL Mints - Verified Doodle owners
50 WL Mints - Spookles community members
10 Mints - Spookles staff + giveaways

Mint Price : 0.09ETH + gas 

Mint proceeds:
- 50% To grow our community (Marketing, Giveaways, Charity) 
- 50% Project Team / Mint Functions / Websites

10% Royalties will be allocated to: 
DoodleBank - 3% 
Community Wallet - 7% (Of which 5% will go into buying of Doodles from Secondary Market to give back to Spookles holders)

Goal: We absolutely love Burnt Toast's art and the Doodles Community! We want to invite doodlers into the Spookles Community. Our future NFT collections will be our own original art and Spookles holders as well as Doodlers will have special access.

Cost: We created 300 unique hand-drawn pieces in our free time and for that, no investment is required from Doodlebank. We used our savings to pay for the minting and website features. Our most desired thing is the love from the community and that magical 'Unofficial Doodrivative' badge.

Accountability: We would love to receive feedback and advise from the founders and the Doodles community. The Spookles community is also actively involved in how we work. We the founders (usually bia, unusually bias, ordinary and typical), will hold custody of the community wallet with standard DAP protocol, voting, multi-sig approval.
